### Configure Playwright HTML reporter output folder in playwright.config.ts

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-reporters-js.md

This JavaScript configuration in `playwright.config.ts` specifies a custom output folder named 'my-report' for the HTML test report. This overrides the default `playwright-report` directory, allowing for organized report storage.

```js
import { defineConfig } from '@playwright/test';

export default defineConfig({
  reporter: [['html', { outputFolder: 'my-report' }]],
});
```

