### Configure Playwright list reporter to print steps

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-reporters-js.md

This example shows how to enhance the 'list' reporter's output by enabling the `printSteps` option within the `playwright.config.ts` file. When `printSteps: true` is set, the reporter will display each test step on its own line, providing more detailed feedback during test execution.

